snippet.title: Ancient Aliens in Colombia
snippet.description: Colombia, The Land of Flowers is known for its amazing natural beauty and friendly people. Today Colombia is a modern country, but it is home to some of the mysterious ancient sites. For example, San Agustín archaeological park contains the largest collection of religious monuments and megalithic sculptures in Latin America. In this playlist, you will see a series of Videos where I explore Ancient Alien influence and if Hinduism had a role in it.

snippet.title: Secrets of Sigiriya, Sri Lanka
snippet.description: Sigiriya is a gigantic, 660 foot tall rock in Sri Lanka. On the rock summit, there are some extraordinary ruins. Historians claim these were built by a King about 1500 years ago, while locals claim it was built by a Mythical King called Ravana. There are many ancient secrets hidden in this location, and I will try to post some of them here.

snippet.description: Sri Lanka is a small, but awesome country with a long history - so long, it is impossible to separate legend and history. Known for its incredible megalithic monuments, the country has been secretly eyed by ancient astronaut theorists, historians and archeologists. Did Gods walk the sacred lands of Sri Lanka? Was it the place of Ravana, an extraterrestrial king mentioned in the Indian Epic Ramayana? Did Lord Buddha visit Sri Lanka to unravel ancient mysteries?

snippet.title: Coral Castle: Everything You Know Is Wrong
snippet.description:
Book by Praveen Mohan "Coral Castle: Everything You Know Is Wrong".

A standard description of Coral Castle goes like this:

Coral Castle is a love monument built by an eccentric man called Edward Leedskalnin. The Castle is a giant doll house built for Ed’s sweet sixteen and his imaginary children. Ed built stone models of household objects like couches, bathtub, cooker, etc. to be used by his fictional family. He also created strange meaningless carvings like the moon fountain and obelisk to impress his lost love. Experts have shown that there is nothing mysterious about the castle or how it was constructed, just one man’s persistent work.
In this book, you will see that all the above statements are false. The chapters ahead will prove beyond any dispute that:
1. Coral Castle was NOT built as a love monument.
2. The Castle is NOT a giant doll house built for Ed’s imaginary family.
3. There are NO meaningless objects in Coral Castle, each one has a specific meaning or purpose. 
4. Opinions of experts and engineers are fundamentally flawed about Coral Castle.

This book was not written to show how Coral Castle was built, but WHY Coral Castle was built. Why did Edward Leedskalnin, a 100 pound man with a 4th grade education, attempt to build the only modern megalithic mystery in the world? 
In addition to this, you will find answers to other burning questions like:
 What is the real meaning of objects like the Barbecue Cooker and Repentance Corner?
 Why did Ed move to the US from Latvia?
 What made Ed carve strange objects like the Stonehenge and Obelisk?
 Why did Ed carve planets and multiple moons side by side?
 Was Ed afflicted with Tuberculosis?
 Why did Ed choose to build Coral Castle in Southern Florida?
 What is the meaning of the drawing on the red door?
 Why did Ed place dozens of rocking chairs all over the Castle?

snippet.title: Giants Existed On Earth - Nephilim Proof
snippet.description: A list of solid evidence proving that we once had a race of Giants. These enormous sized beings were the offspring of angels and humans and their skeletons have been unearthed all over the world. The Book of Enoch, Bible, Ramayana, Avesta and many ancient texts around the world confirm this. In the United States, hundreds of Giant skeletons have been found under ancient mounds. In the Bible, these Giants are referred to as Nephilim. Enjoy your stay!
